@startuml 01-basic-cc-view
!include ../../../../../../tooling/styles/plantuml/structural/package-diagram-style.iuml

!theme plain

title Component-and-Connector View: Basic Structure

package "Runtime System" {
    component "Component A" as CA {
        portin "Input\nPort" as CA_in
        portout "Output\nPort" as CA_out
    }
    
    component "Component B" as CB {
        portin "Input\nPort" as CB_in
        portout "Output\nPort" as CB_out
    }
    
    component "Component C" as CC {
        portin "Input\nPort" as CC_in
    }
    
    rectangle "<<connector>>\nConnector 1" as CON1 {
    }
    
    rectangle "<<connector>>\nConnector 2" as CON2 {
    }
}

CA_out --> CON1 : attachment
CON1 --> CB_in : attachment
CB_out --> CON2 : attachment
CON2 --> CC_in : attachment

note right of CA
  **Components**
  Principal processing 
  units and data stores
end note

note right of CON1
  **Connectors**
  Pathways of 
  interaction
end note

note bottom of CA_out
  **Ports**
  Interaction points
  of components
end note

legend right
  |= Symbol |= Meaning |
  | <#E3F2FD> Component | Processing unit or data store |
  | <#FFF8E1> Connector | Interaction pathway |
  | Port | Interface for attachment |
  | Arrow | Attachment relation |
endlegend

@enduml
